Job Describe:
1.Design and implement Computer vision / Machine learning algorithm for industrial robot;
2.Design and implement user interface for vision software.
3.	Cooperate with a cross-function team to develop smart features in robot applications;
4.Maintain, debug and document developed codes.
Basic Requirements:
1.Enthusiasm for building state-of-the-art robots with intelligent vision system;
2.Strong coding skills in C and C++;
3.Experience in developing computer vision / machine learning algorithms
Plus:
1. Strong knowledge on camera calibration, camera geometry and robot’s hand/eye system
2. Familiar with Visual Studio, QT, and OpenCV

1.運用深度學習(deep learning)和機器學習，開發影像識別，語義分析，語音識別等人工智慧演算法
2.具機器學習(machine learning)、圖形識別(pattern recognition)等研究背景與知識
3.熟悉 C++ 及其 STL
4.熟悉常用機器學習算法;
5.對深度學習基本原理有扎實理解;
6.良好的溝通能力及團隊合作的特質
